title: Won 9 of my placement matches and got placed in Silver 5
body: I think this is kind of stupid and i'm wondering whats up, last season I won 4 games and got placed in Silver 5 but seriously winning 9 and not having a bad score in almost all the games yet I get this, so yea just wondering is this normal at all

replies.body: Be happy u got silver 5 with 9 wins, i won 10 time and got b5. Id love to be silver 5 with my wins
Sucks, I wonder why this is happening though it's kinda bullshit
